WEBVTT

00:02.390 --> 00:03.869
Previously on The Shield.

00:04.070 --> 00:06.743
- Sir, what's the problem?
- My dick. Please.

00:06.950 --> 00:08.781
You're caught in a rat trap.

00:08.990 --> 00:11.663
I've got lupus. Had it for 15 years.

00:13.150 --> 00:14.708
Claudette. Oh, my God.

00:14.910 --> 00:16.787
Don't move her. Call the paramedics.

00:16.990 --> 00:20.027
Why didn't you tell me that Sadie
has a history of mental illness?

00:20.230 --> 00:22.505
I need a life for myself.
You been missing me?

00:22.710 --> 00:23.665
Ex-wife.

00:23.870 --> 00:28.022
I wasn't worth taking care of
and now I'm not worth shit. You...

00:28.230 --> 00:30.824
- I wanna go home.
- At least we found his weak spot.

00:32.350 --> 00:33.783
Shit, go.

00:33.990 --> 00:35.742
Hey!

00:35.950 --> 00:37.463
You. You're under arrest...

00:37.670 --> 00:40.901
...for possession of heroin
with intent to distribute.

00:41.110 --> 00:44.386
The price is simple. I help you
put away these fine young men...

00:44.590 --> 00:47.468
...you make sure you put them away
right here.

00:47.670 --> 00:48.898
You send Lem to Lompoc...

00:49.110 --> 00:51.624
...you're the murderer.
- I had a conversation with Antwon.

00:51.830 --> 00:55.106
You're bluffing. You don't have the
stomach to serve Lem up to Antwon.

00:55.310 --> 00:56.789
I didn't used to.

